## The Experiment Lifecycle (Detailed)

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  PROPOSED                                     │
│  Agent writes hypothesis in changelog.md      │
│  Agent creates entry in experiments log       │
│  Status: "proposed"                           │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────┘
                   │
                   ▼ (auto-evolve? → apply immediately)
                   ▼ (framework change? → wait for human approval)
                   │
┌──────────────────┴───────────────────────────┐
│  ACTIVE                                       │
│  Change applied to methodology.md             │
│  Status: "active"                             │
│  Running for N iterations (default: 3)        │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────┘
                   │
                   ▼ (after N iterations, calculate metric delta)
                   │
          ┌────────┴────────┐
          │                 │
          ▼                 ▼
   ┌──────────┐      ┌──────────┐
   │  KEEP    │      │ DISCARD  │
   │          │      │          │
   │ Update   │      │ Revert   │
   │ method.  │      │ method.  │
   │ to v+1   │      │ to v     │
   └──────────┘      └──────────┘
```

