## Quick-Start Template

Copy this into a `program.md` for any new project:

```markdown
# [Project Name] — Autoresearch Program

## Domain
[What you're researching]

## Output
[What each iteration produces]

## Metric
[Your composite score formula]

Metric = ___ × ______ + ___ × ______ + ___ × ______

## Infrastructure (Fixed — Do Not Modify)
- [What's being studied — the universe]
- [The evaluation function]
- [The constraints]

## Experiment Surface (Agent Modifies)
- [The methodology document the agent evolves]

## Keep/Discard Rules
- Auto-evolve: [list what the agent can change freely]
- Requires approval: [list what needs human sign-off]

## Experiment Loop
LOOP:
1. Read current state (methodology version, recent scores)
2. Propose ONE change (write hypothesis first)
3. Apply the change
4. Run the iteration
5. Measure against metric
6. Keep (if improved or simpler) / Discard (if worse)
7. Log to results + changelog
8. Repeat

## Baseline
[First run score — everything is measured against this]

## Never Stop
Once started, run indefinitely until manually stopped.
```

